title: AHS Apocalypse Episode 3 Review SPOILERS!!
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This episode was out of this world, the season keeps getting better and better every episode!
This season will be the best ever, the fight sequence reminds me of kill bill Adina Porter and Kathy Bates are bad ass

The scene between Mallory and Michael reminded me of the end of Asylum with sister Jude and Lana Winters 
“If you look in the face of evil, evils going to look right back at you”
omg is Constance’s mind programmed into Ms.Mead? 👀

This might be crazy. But after Mallory is resurrected her eyesight is normal and she doesn’t need her glasses. What if that’s the first subtle hint Mallory is the next supreme? After all, a future supreme has glowing health.
